ival reference locally unless the exact old name matters.\\n- Delete superseded local `codex*` worktrees after archiving any uncommitted local-only files.\\n\\n## Worktree policy\\n\\n- One active task should map to one dedicated worktree.\\n- When a branch is being renamed or merged, keep a local pre-merge archive branch until verification passes.\\n- Remove finished temporary worktrees after the branch is clean and pushed.\\n- Do not keep stray helper clones or borrowed clones once a canonical clone exists on both PC and `dev-intern-02`.\\n\\n## Verification checklist\\n\\n- `git status --short --branch`\\n- `git log --oneline --decorate --max-count 20`\\n- Verify the intended branch name before pushing.\\n- If branch cleanup touches GitHub, confirm local archival refs exist first.\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave2/memory-guardrails/stdout.log:44:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_23\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc \\\"grep -RIn --exclude-dir=.git -E 'proposal|attention|center|topk|K_g|num_proposals|queries|query_tokens|gaussian|memory' node_controller plans scripts vae_poc 2>/dev/null | head -n 800\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"node_controller/controller.py:239:            [\\\"nvidia-smi\\\", \\\"--query-gpu=index,utilization.gpu,memory.used,memory.total,temperature.gpu\\\",\\nnode_controller/volc_dispatcher_entry.sh:45:  \\\"command\\\": [\\\"bash\\\", \\\"-lc\\\", \\\"hostname && nvidia-smi --query-gpu=index,name,memory.total,memory.used,utilization.gpu --format=csv,noheader && echo SMOKE_OK\\\"],\\nplans/big-plan.md:101:2. use causal attention to establish prefix dependence among these latents\\nplans/big-plan.md:102:3. when generating the current block, read from the prefix latent memory rather than the full token history\\nplans/big-plan.md:118:Once the scaffold and compact latent memory are available, the next stage generates the detail