\\n/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn/summary.md:621:- `K_g = 64`\\n/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn/summary.md:622:- `num_proposal_blocks = 2`\\n/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn/summary.md:629:2. pooled proposal mode\\n/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn/summary.md:633:That preserves the current model contract, gives a clear migration path, and keeps the expensive part local and bounded instead of accidentally reintroducing an `O(M^2)` attention wall.\\n/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn/launch.json:4:  \\\"agent_name\\\": \\\"proposal-attn\\\",\\n/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn/launch.json:11:  \\\"prompt_path\\\": \\\"/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn/prompt.md\\\",\\n/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn/launch.json:12:  \\\"stdout_log\\\": \\\"/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn/stdout.log\\\",\\n/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn/launch.json:13:  \\\"last_message\\\": \\\"/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn/last_message.txt\\\",\\n/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn/launch.json:14:  \\\"status_path\\\": \\\"/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn/status.json\\\"\\n/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn/run_agent.sh:3:AGENT_ROOT=/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn\\n/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn/run_agent.sh:5:TMP_BIN=\\\"/tmp/codex_proposal-attn_$$\\\"\\n/dev_vepfs/rc_wu/codex_subagents/20260328_mesh_center_wave1/proposal-attn/run_agent.sh:6:PROMPT_PAT